                "p2",
                "verse",
                "v10",
                "note",
                "f"
              ],
              "value": "tn Heb “for therefore I have seen your face like seeing the face of God and you have accepted me.”\nsn This is an allusion to the preceding episode (32:22-31) in which Jacob saw the face of God and realized his prayer was answered."
