              "rowId": 68,
              "keyParts": [
                68,
                "p2",
                "verse",
                "v11",
                "note",
                "f"
              ],
              "value": "tn Heb “blessing.” It is as if Jacob is trying to repay what he stole from his brother twenty years earlier."
            },
            {
              "rowId": 69,
              "keyParts": [
                69,
                "p2",
                "verse",
                "v11",
                "content"
              ],
              "value": "that was brought to you, for God has been generous"
